data.description: Beautiful Oakdale Bluffs Community is the perfect place to call home!! Did you know End Units are the Best Investment?! Well this end-unit is absolutely beautiful...one owner, well-lit, and meticulously maintained. The open concept townhome has it all including swim/tennis and a clubhouse located near the river. The community is 5 minutes from Reformation Brewery, near several parks, easy interstate access, close to Smyrna Market Village, Upper Westside Village and Vinings. Last but not least...the community has its own entrance to the Riverline Park! Offering 4 spacious bedrooms, 3.5 baths. Stainless steel appliances, hardwood & ceramic tile floors on the main floor.
